##  Verificación

### Verificar Tunnel0 GRE
```cisco
show interfaces Tunnel0
```

### Verificar SA IKEv2
```cisco
show crypto ikev2 sa
```

### Verificar IPSec — protocolo GRE (47) en SA
```cisco
show crypto ipsec sa
```
Buscar:
```
local  ident (addr/mask/prot/port): (200.0.0.2/255.255.255.255/47/0)
```

### Verificar OSPF
```cisco
show ip ospf neighbor
show ip route ospf
```

### Verificar paquetes cifrados
```cisco
show crypto ipsec sa | include encaps|decaps
```

### Ping de prueba
```
PC1> ping 10.10.2.100
```


